source.data:
@Hooks
Feature: Purchase From Outfitters

  @Test1
  Scenario: User Purchases a Biker Leather Jacket

    Given I open the outfitters website
    And I navigate to the most popular section
    When I click on the faux leather biker jacket
    Then I should see product details page
    And I click on the size xl
    When I click on view cart button
    Then I should see cart page
    And I click on checkout button
    And I enter email
    And I enter First Name
    And I enter Last Name
    And I enter Address
    And I enter City
    And I enter Postal code

  @Test2
  Scenario: User Purchases a Shirt

  Given Saad is on outfitters website
  And Saad click on search button
  And Saad enter "shirts" in search term
  And Saad click on "check shirt"
  And Saad select "medium" size
  And Saad click on add to cart button
  And Saad select view cart option
  And Saad enter the first name
  And Saad enter the last name
  And Saad enter the address
  And Saad enter the city
  And Saad enter the postal code
  Then Saad proceed to checkout
  And Saad review the order details

  @Test3
  Scenario: User Purchases a Polo shirt

    Given User is on outfitters website
    And User click on search button
    And User enter "polo" in search term
    And User click on "solid polo shirt"
    And User select "medium" size
    And User click on add to cart button
    And User select view cart option
    Then User should see shopping cart page
    And User select checkout
    Then User should see customer information page
    And User enter the first name
    And User enter the last name
    And User enter the address
    And User enter the city
    And User enter the postal code
    Then User proceed to checkout
    And User review the order details

  @Test4
  Scenario: User purchases a slim fit jeans

      Given User is on outfitters website
      And User click on search button
      And User enter "jeans" in search term
      And User click on "slim fit jeans"
      And User select "30" size
      And User click on add to cart button
      And User select view cart option
      Then User should see shopping cart page
      And User select checkout
      Then User should see customer information page
      And User enter the first name
      And User enter the last name
      And User enter the address
      And User enter the city
      And User enter the postal code
      Then User proceed to checkout
      And User review the order details

  @Test5
  Scenario: User purchases a skinny comfort jeans

       Given User is on outfitters website
       And User click on search button
       And User enter "jeans" in search term
       And User click on "skinny comfort jeans"
       And User select "30" size
       And User click on add to cart button
       And User select view cart option
       Then User should see shopping cart page
       And User select checkout
       Then User should see customer information page
       And User enter the first name
       And User enter the last name
       And User enter the address
       And User enter the city
       And User enter the postal code
       Then User proceed to checkout
       And User review the order details

  @Test6
  Scenario: Saad purchases a basic jogger trouser

    Given Saad is on outfitters website
    And Saad click on search button
    And Saad enter "trousers" in search term
    And Saad click on "basic jogger trouser"
    And Saad select "30" size
    And Saad click on add to cart button
    And Saad select view cart option
    Then Saad should see shopping cart page
    And Saad select checkout
    Then Saad should see customer information page
    And Saad enter the first name
    And Saad enter the last name
    And Saad enter the address
    And Saad enter the city
    And Saad enter the postal code
    Then Saad proceed to checkout
    And Saad review the order details

  @Test7
  Scenario: Saad purchases a linen bermuda shorts

    Given Saad is on outfitters website
    And Saad click on search button
    And Saad enter "shorts" in search term
    And Saad click on "linen bermuda shorts"
    And Saad select "30" size
    And Saad click on add to cart button
    And Saad select view cart option
    Then Saad should see shopping cart page
    And Saad select checkout
    Then Saad should see customer information page
    And Saad enter the first name
    And Saad enter the last name
    And Saad enter the address
    And Saad enter the city
    And Saad enter the postal code
    Then Saad proceed to checkout
    And Saad review the order details

  @Test8
  Scenario: Saad purchases a regular fit co-ord set with zipper jacket

    Given Saad is on outfitters website
    And Saad click on search button
    And Saad enter "co-ord set" in search term
    And Saad click on "regular fit co-ord set with zipper jacket"
    And Saad select "medium" size
    And Saad click on add to cart button
    And Saad select view cart option
    Then Saad should see shopping cart page
    And Saad select checkout
    Then Saad should see customer information page
    And Saad enter the first name
    And Saad enter the last name
    And Saad enter the address
    And Saad enter the city
    And Saad enter the postal code
    Then Saad proceed to checkout
    And Saad review the order details

  @Test9
  Scenario: Iqra purchases good vibes fragrance

      Given Iqra is on outfitters website
      And Iqra click on search button
      And Iqra enter "fragrances" in search term
      And Iqra click on "good vibes fragrance"
      And Iqra click on add to cart button
      And Iqra select view cart option
      Then Iqra should see shopping cart page
      And Iqra select checkout
      Then Iqra should see customer information page
      And Iqra enter the first name
      And Iqra enter the last name
      And Iqra enter the address
      And Iqra enter the city
      And Iqra enter the postal code
      Then Iqra proceed to checkout
      And Iqra review the order details

  @Test10
  Scenario: Muhammad purchases dark knight fragrance

    Given Muhammad is on outfitters website
    And Muhammad click on search button
    And Muhammad enter "fragrances" in search term
    And Muhammad click on "dark knight fragrance"
    And Muhammad click on add to cart button
    And Muhammmad select view cart option
    Then Muhammad should see shopping cart page
    And Muhammad select checkout
    Then Muhammad should see customer information page
    And Muhammad enter the first name
    And Muhammad enter the last name
    And Muhammad enter the address
    And Muhammad enter the city
    And Muhammad enter the postal code
    Then Muhammad proceed to checkout
    And Muhammad review the order details
